The "'''BoSS code'''" was a complex and intricate code of conduct for [[Starship/Legends|starships]] and their crews imposed by the [[Bureau of Ships and Services/Legends|Bureau of Ships and Services]]. So complicated was the code that no organic being was capable of knowing its complete intricacies, and often droids, such as [[LE manifest droid]]s, were used by starship [[Captain/Legends|captains]] to help them obey the BoSS code.<ref name="The New Essential Guide to Droids">''[[The New Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

